full_description: inovex is an IT project center driven by innovation and quality, focusing its services on Digital Transformation. Around 500 IT experts provide companies with comprehensive support in the digitalisation and agilisation of their core business and in the implementation of new digital use cases. The range of solutions includes Data & AI, Application Development, Development of IT Infrastructure, Replatforming, IT Security and trainings (inovex Academy).

